title: Neta Furi Shitetara Gouin Ecchi - Honki ni Naru made Daite Ii?
description: After moving to Tokyo, Totsuka Azusa's daily life had changed into nothing. For her, people left company because of marriage or due to their own circumstances. After dinner, she felt a presence of someone beside her on the bed... It was the guy next door!

related.title: Crawling Into Me in the Middle of the Night (Official Colored)
